{"tid":2498373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實根據支那小粉紅平時嘅準則，Marvel套尚氣係辱華到仆街","createTime":"2021-04-21T06:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T06:50:14.000Z","uid":321977,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"84b723da24151867c13a869449c792f1f103bc73","tid":2498373,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:14:31.000Z","msg":"演員已經辱華<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pTTvF3C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpTTvF3C.png&h=019fe559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jt65u4y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJt65u4y.jpg&h=cef6aea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n撞樣翠翠嘅主角<br />\n同支共啲高官一樣<br />\n支那出世但外套護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mc43gCZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmc43gCZ.png&h=16581a87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對家係靚仔過佢好撚多嘅梁朝偉<br />\n英籍香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ntrailer啲對白都可以辱華<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mhso05W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmhso05W.png&h=84ba8607&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNhcUqX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNhcUqX.png&h=69cf39d0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fuj3gEi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffuj3gEi.png&h=e090fc6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n支那過咗咁多年都仲要靠香港呢隻白手套<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ea0YP0K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEa0YP0K.png&h=ca546b05&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2m9cd7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2m9cd7.png&h=6c6b20a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WT9yDUa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWT9yDUa.png&h=1cece359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁朝偉係主角個老豆<br />\n香港都早過共產黨出現<br />\n支那可以話係食香港嘅奶粉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bb0eom0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbb0eom0.jpg&h=6b05f644&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最重要係梁朝偉型撚過主角太多<br />\n大部分人都話似翠翠嘅主角唔撚掂成個路人咁，係咁屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMarvel呢次選角真係錯撚哂<br />\n一係你唔好簡個似翠翠嘅演員<br />\n一係你就簡個唔好咁撚型嘅反派啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個戲名又撚柒，比人話尚氣唔接下氣<br />\n小粉紅出征未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YDQqu4K.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYDQqu4K.gif&h=473d6099&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ee7de42dc4be0de63c0947f0682b4e86712badd","tid":2498373,"uid":70527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:20:20.000Z","msg":"仲有個女主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e089f03b2cc0a7709673074ba90c198e913f63","tid":2498373,"uid":82068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:26:02.000Z","msg":"英屬香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53aadbd0ad154456e09cc86d80e3d5c93c276ad","tid":2498373,"uid":99962,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:29:33.000Z","msg":"果位男主角個樣似上水走水貨既大陸人"},{"pid":"a337c1dc845ef7251677bcddd722fd0f89669831","tid":2498373,"uid":250511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e53aadbd0ad154456e09cc86d80e3d5c93c276ad","tid":2498373